  "dateModified": "2026-04-27",
  "datePublished": "2026-04-27",
  "description": "The structural condition in which a system can no longer absorb additional load without strain — the variety of disturbances arriving from the system's environment has begun to exceed the variety of internal states the system can use to absorb them.",
